{"tid":971493,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人20幾歲覺得自己老態橫生","createTime":"2019-01-06T16:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T16:58:45.000Z","uid":126697,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e23a7a6c7b9f2cfdfcfaf6e2d0d21a83a26e51","tid":971493,"uid":126697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:19:46.000Z","msg":"跑兩步行幾級樓梯都喘氣<br />\n以後就打幾個鐘波都仲好有精力。<br />\n<br />\n思想與行動都多左顧慮<br />\n唔似以前咁話做就做。<br />\n<br />\n身邊朋友結婚既結婚<br />\n生小朋友既生小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n個個出到黎聚會係傾生活上的辛酸<br />\n唔再係一班人嘻嘻哈哈係到劈酒。<br />\n<br />\n以前要諗點樣係屋企偷走出街去party<br />\n而家就要諗點樣係party偷走番屋企休息。<br />\n<br />\n我坐左係張櫈到，望住從前既一班嚫仔，到而家個個呀叔咁既樣，先覺得時間好似過得好快，話唔定下一次有呢種同樣既感覺，大家已經滿頭白髮。<br />\n<br />\n珍惜當下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨係諗埋啲咁既野都覺得自己老餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1dec253d4667492dccc556e6e9da3664d5b47c8","tid":971493,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"只係代表咗你已經成長咗, 唔再係啲o靚仔"},{"pid":"eabbf8ef9cf439283b4d630a86b7dda92a61c298","tid":971493,"uid":151512,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"你廢姐"},{"pid":"ec8d15f550f20fc40444a37c9d3253d9ff02d825","tid":971493,"uid":50328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3c4a11d2504a7dddab38228a12d9d3fff556ae1","tid":971493,"uid":210161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"Me<br />\n<br />\n廿幾歲<br />\n幾年冇做運動<br />\n<br />\n近幾個月開始周身骨痛 頸椎尾龍骨周不時移位 <br />\n免疫力好差 出疹 之後生埋蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*運動好重要<br />\n身體一差就病痛就會連住黎"},{"pid":"39c692128a1309f140ed789b93b94274b1fc0f7b","tid":971493,"uid":220174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:42:2